  "title": "Painter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Perform surface preparation, paint mixing, and coating application to deliver high-quality finishes while maintaining a safe and organized work environment and collaborating effectively with team members and clients.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare surfaces by cleaning, sanding, and repairing to ensure proper paint adhesion</li><li>Select and blend paints to achieve specific colors and finishes according to project requirements</li><li>Apply paint, stain, and other coatings using brushes, rollers, and sprayers to deliver consistent, high-quality results</li><li>Handle materials such as wood, metal, and drywall safely and appropriately during painting tasks</li><li>Maintain a clean and organized workspace to promote safety and efficiency</li><li>Communicate clearly with clients, team members, and other professionals to coordinate work and address concerns</li><li>Manage time effectively to complete painting tasks within set deadlines</li><li>Identify and resolve issues during the painting process to maintain quality standards</li><li>Attend daily Tool Box meetings to stay informed on safety and work updates</li></ul>",
